Package: sigdiscov
Type: Package
Title: Pairwise Moran's I for Spatial Transcriptomics
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2024-01-18
Authors@R: c(
    person("Peng", "Jiang", email = "pengj@alumni.princeton.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Seongyong", "Park", role = "ctb"))
Description: Compute pairwise Moran's I statistics between genes in spatial
    transcriptomics data. Uses optimized BLAS matrix operations for high
    performance computation. Supports both dense and sparse matrices.
